headline: The Top 5 Analyst Questions From Bristol-Myers Squibb’s Q1 Earnings Call
summary: Bristol-Myers Squibb’s first quarter results reflected a blend of strong execution in its newer growth portfolio and ongoing pressure from generic competition in legacy products.
